snippet.title: EVE Online: Onslaught - Feature Tour
snippet.description:
EVE Online: Onslaught, the new expansion, is live! This feature tour video includes a breathtaking look at new Abyssal Deadspace co-op and PvP, new Triglavian ships, Upwell navigation structures, Activity Tracker and more. Play EVE for free at http://www.eveonline.com.

Your galactic adventure awaits
Join the #1 Space MMO 

To learn more about EVE Online: Onslaught head to http://eveonline.com/now/onslaught
